    {
      "text": "folder 57 - 041\nR-2\n\n___ I have figured it out - on the basis of Galina's dream in \"DI\" - specifically to whom I assigned the dream - i.e. the pisceses fish + the pitcher of water, aquarius, that replaces the cruel misuse of the fish. Galina is the wife of the head of the CP USSR; she is Pilate's wife. I interpret this dream thus: Galina symbolizes the good or idealistic side of the Empire (Rome/CP/USSR). (The dream clearly rejects pisces + ushers in the new age of sharing + brotherhood: the pit",
      "matched_alias": "Pilate",
